==English==
===Noun===
'''attributive'''
#(''grammar'') A [[word]] or [[phrase]], such as an [[adjective]], that is [[placed]] [[adjacent]] to the [[noun]] it [[modifies]] without a [[linking]] [[verb]]
#* Thus ''black and white'' in ''the black and white dog'', or ''Bengal'' in ''the Bengal tiger''

===Adjective===
'''attributive'''
#(''grammar'') of, or being an attributive (as above)
#having the nature of an [[attribute]]
